com.coveros.selenified.element

Class WaitFor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.coveros.selenified.element.WaitFor

  • public class WaitFor
extends Object
    WaitFor performs dynamic waits on a particular element, until a particular condition is met. Nothing is ever returned. The default wait is 5 seconds, but can be overridden. If the condition is not met in the allotted time, still nothing is returned, but an error is logged
    Version:
    3.0.4
    Author:
    Max Saperstone
